Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 9:49 AM ET
Equity Real Estate Investment Trusts (REITs)

Company Overview of Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc. focuses on investing in corporate properties that are leased to credit worthy tenants under long-term net leases in the United States. As of December 31, 2016, it operated seven retail properties and two office properties. The company qualifies as a real estate investment trust for federal income tax purposes. It generally would not be subject to federal corporate income taxes if it distributes at least 90% of its taxable income to its stockholders. The company was formerly known as Rich Uncles REIT, Inc. and changed its name to Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc. in October 2015. The company was founded in 2015 and is based in Costa Mesa, California.


3080 Bristol StreetSuite 550Costa Mesa, CA 92626United StatesFounded in 201532 Employees



