Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc. Key Developments

Rich Uncles Mulls Acquisitions
Apr 3 17
Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc. is looking for acquisitions. Rich Uncles expect to use substantially all of the net proceeds from the offering to acquire and manage a portfolio of real estate investments.



Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc. announced delayed annual 10-K filing
Apr 3 17
On 04/03/2017, Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-K by the deadline required by the SEC.


Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc. Completes Acquisition of Newly-Renovated Office Facility Located South of Cape Canaveral
Mar 10 17
Rich Uncles NNN REIT, Inc. announced that it had completed the acquisition of newly-renovated office facility located south of Cape Canaveral in the Space Coast region of Florida with triple net tenant Northrop Grumman.


