REPLYRich Uncles says:August 3rd, 2016 at 10:32 amYour facts are incorrect.  We are indeed a public company but not traded on a stock exchange – by our choice.  Publicly traded REITs perform like any other stock, namely, they are volatile.  Rich Uncles is a public non-listed REIT where the value of our portfolio is determined by the Net Asset Value of our properties.  We believe this is a much better structure.




